text: Baa Baa Black sheep have you any wool?
Yes I can spare 3 bags full.
One for the King and one for the dame
One for the little boy that plays down the lane
Baa Baa Gray sheep have you any wool?
Yes I can spare 3 bags full.
One for the Master and one for the Dame
One for the little man that works down the lane
Baa Baa White sheep have you any wool?
Yes I can spare 3 bags full.
One for my family one for the Queen
One for the pretty girl who loves to sing
